Package OOBN

Class Summary
BNEPanel A panel containing a Bayesian Network Editor.
Bridge This class translates between OOBN data types and OKBC data types.
CPTDialog  
CPTPanel A conditional probability table is a display of a conditional probability distribution.
DFEDialog  
DFEPanel A Distribution Function Editor is a browser-editor for unconditional probability distributions.
DiscreteRandomVariable  
DoubleVector A DoubleVector is a vector whose elements are of type double.
FiniteRandomVariable  
IntVector An IntVector is a vector whose elements are of type int.
OOBN This is the entry point for the OOBN browser-editor, at least during development.
OOBNClass  
OOBNComplexSlot A complex slot is one whose value type is an OOBNClass, rather than a random variable.
OOBNNode An OOBNNode graphically represents an OOBNSlot in the graph of a Bayesian network.
OOBNSimpleSlot A simple slot is one whose value type is a random variable, rather than an OOBNClass.
OOBNSlot A slot must be either a simple slot or a complex slot.
StubBNEPanel Use this panel as a substitute if BNEPanel isn't working.
Utilities This class is the home for some static methods.
